{"tid":2177430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"侵: Biden同我debate前要驗下佢有無食禁藥先","createTime":"2020-08-27T17:06:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-29T02:58:38.000Z","uid":270889,"like":124,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"3fec86378ce642cc265bd37f77f65c40f5aca0a8","tid":2177430,"uid":270889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T17:06:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/thehill/status/1299025404729200640?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fthehill%2Fstatus%2F1299025404729200640%3Fs%3D20&d=Bx5vHrS2V4FMjGMjdccONnXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=c0c383ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fthehill%2Fstatus%2F1299025404729200640%3Fs%3D20&h=70168184\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/thehill/status/1299025404729200640?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\nPresident Trump is <span class=\"red\">calling for drug tests to be administered before his first presidential debate</span> with Democratic nominee Joe Biden next month.<br />\n<br />\nTrump made the demand in an Oval Office interview with the Washington Examiner on Wednesday, saying he noticed a <span class=\"red\">sudden improvement in Biden&rsquo;s primary debate performance</span> against Sen. Bernie Sanders (I-Vt.) in March. He offered no evidence to support his suggestion that the improvement could have been the result of drugs. <br />\n<br />\n&quot;Nobody thought that he was even going to win,&quot; Trump said. &quot;Because his debate performances were so bad. Frankly, his best performance was against Bernie. <span class=\"red\">We're going to call for a drug test</span>, by the way, because his best performance was against Bernie. It wasn't that he was Winston Churchill because he wasn't, but it was a normal, boring debate. You know, nothing amazing happened. And we are going to call for a drug test because there's no way &mdash; you can't do that.&quot; <br />\n<br />\n&quot;I don't know how he could have been so incompetent in his debate performances and then all of a sudden be OK against Bernie,&quot; he added when pressed to clarify. &quot;My point is, if you go back and watch some of those numerous debates, he was so bad. He wasn't even coherent. And against Bernie, he was. And we're calling for a drug test.&quot; <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所羅門: 你都知ChinaJoe實出醜<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SolomonYue/status/1299023645256253440?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSolomonYue%2Fstatus%2F1299023645256253440%3Fs%3D20&d=Bx5vHrS2V4FMjGMjdccONnXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=bc8ac337\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSolomonYue%2Fstatus%2F1299023645256253440%3Fs%3D20&h=cfd12cc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SolomonYue/status/1299023645256253440?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n左膠: 侵根本唔值得我地同佢debate呀 hi <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/EricBoehlert/status/1299026394442235905?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FEricBoehlert%2Fstatus%2F1299026394442235905%3Fs%3D20&d=Bx5vHrS2V4FMjGMjdccONnXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=e636029a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FEricBoehlert%2Fstatus%2F1299026394442235905%3Fs%3D20&h=dc5d448e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/EricBoehlert/status/1299026394442235905?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"bd39536f1ffb3bf6a21c3fc17d0ade410a7b81f9","tid":2177430,"uid":270889,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T17:10:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/michaelahrens/status/1299017637867986945?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmichaelahrens%2Fstatus%2F1299017637867986945%3Fs%3D20&d=Bx5vHrS2V4FMjGMjdccONnXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=f53c998d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fm